學科別分類



中文摘要
觀光產業被視為21世紀明星及無煙囪產業，世界各國無不極力推展，在宜蘭童玩節打響宜蘭知名度後，台灣各地觀光活動如雨後春筍般發展，尤其是產業觀光活動，既可以推展觀光又可以行銷當地一級農、漁特產，增加就業機會，因此；各縣市政府無不投註經費及人力辦理。     七股地區擁有豐富天然資源如全台最大的潟湖、黑面琵鷺與七股鹽山而聞名全台，七股海產街也曾聞名一時。七股潟湖歷經七股工業區及臺南縣濱南工業區開發計畫案引發各界關註，最後因未通過相關法規而終止。1997年首次辦理搭竹筏遊潟湖及摸文蛤體驗活動，事隔10年後；地方政府為促進當地產業的行銷與特殊生態保育辦理「觀光赤嘴園」，該活動地點為早期漁民採集野生赤嘴(環文蛤)的地點，辦理觀光赤嘴園摸文蛤體驗活動，除希望帶來觀光效益外也希望喚起民眾對環境保育的認知。活動迄今已辦理6年，每年均吸引相當人潮參加。     本文以臺南市七股觀光赤嘴園為例，探討國家機關與社會資本間治理互賴情形，研究發現1、基層產業觀光活動需具有當地特色性 2、需藉由政府及社區間相互信賴、合作共同配合辦理，3、因資源有限，地方與政府應努力朝資源整合方向邁進才能順利及持續辦理。


英文摘要
Almost every country has spared no effort on the developments of tourism, because the industry of tourism is considered to be the most blooming business in twenty one century and as a non-chimney industry.Lots of activities of tourism have been sprung up like mushrooms in Taiwan after the great success and reputations on “Yilan international children’s folklore & folkgame festival”, especially the sightseeing industry and activities. These tourism activities not only upgrade and increase the value of local agriculture and fishery products, but also can bring more employment opportunities, all above will be achieved just by growing tourism, therefore, most of the local governments have spent any amount of human resources and expenses on it.      Cigu is famous for the abundance of natural resources, such as the lagoon, black-faced spoonbills and Cigu Salt Mountain, also the Cigu seafood street was once popular. People ever paid attention to Cigu lagoon because of the development projects of Cigu and Binnan industrial parks in Tainan County, but the projects was terminated by the failure of relative statutes in the end. In 1997, the first activity of experience of rafting across the lagoon and clamming was held, after 10 years, in order to promote the marketing of local industries and special ecology care, the local government had set “The touring park of Cyclina Sinesis” where was the fishers collected wild Cyclina Sinesis. The reason for holding the experience of clamming in Touring park of Cyclina Sinesis is not only looking forward to enhancing the benefits in tourism but also raising public consciousness of ecological preservation. It has been held for six years, and has attracted lots of people every year.        The Cigu touring park of Cyclina Sinesis in Tainan County is such an example to discuss the cooperative relationship between the national organizations and the social economics, by the research we found: 1.	It’s necessary for those basic tourist activities to be characteristic locally.2.	The activity needs the government and communities to assist and cooperate with each other.3.	Due to the limitation of resources, if the activity would like to be growing and blooming, local and government should work harder on the resource integration.


